{"tid":2150721,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】《3日2夜》女主持水上摔角玩到癲　張曦雯毛里裘斯有艷遇","createTime":"2020-08-11T05:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T07:04:05.000Z","uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"450106695f2b203637e173b708ee12bee7b24059","tid":2150721,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:15:57.000Z","msg":"夏日炎炎，最好的消暑活動當然是游一下水減壓消下暑。今日TVB更加找了《3日2夜》中幾位的主持：陳婉衡(Alycia)、朱智賢、張曦雯(Kelly)、鄭衍峰、鄺潔楹(Judy)、潘梓鋒、周佩婷進行記者會，大玩水上活動。而幾位主持在船戰搶旗及水上摔角中玩得非常投入。炎夏之中，看她們玩水的確是賞心樂事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qvNsi7V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqvNsi7V.jpg&h=72b66d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5kUJzB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5kUJzB.jpg&h=0d1d4804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xkmozC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xkmozC.jpg&h=c6aed4b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wpa9xsY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpa9xsY.jpg&h=2b852e6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpdCGmk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpdCGmk.jpg&h=ef274fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/109357/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-3%E6%97%A52%E5%A4%9C-%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%91%94%E8%A7%92%E7%8E%A9%E5%88%B0%E7%99%B2-%E5%BC%B5%E6%9B%A6%E9%9B%AF%E6%AF%9B%E9%87%8C%E8%A3%98%E6%96%AF%E6%9C%89%E8%89%B7%E9%81%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F109357%2F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2596-3%25E6%2597%25A52%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2591%2594%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%2588%2